Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Umaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of cake should we have for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hanging out with friends this year,\Nso don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.38,0:00:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,O-oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.25,0:00:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother! If you're gonna make a cake again next year,\Nyou should make a Santa doll too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.79,0:00:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,On second thought, I WILL have cake\Non the 25th so go on, make one!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.67,0:00:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,R-really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude, you're making a cake from scratch?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.17,0:02:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're better than most DADS.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I enjoy it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.58,0:02:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Taihei, if little Tanukichi wasn't around,\Nyou'd have nothing to do and just shrivel up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it looks like we won't have to work\Novertime today, so how about we go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're overdue to join us, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to a Christmas concert of anime songs.\NWould you like to come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanoshiku nareba ii desu wa\NIf you can enjoy yourself, that will be good indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sore nara kitto kachi desu wa\NDo that, and you're sure to win indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just us three?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.29,0:02:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Christmas will be kinda boring without Tanukichi around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we SHOULD go to that concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,O-okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Christmas indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm fine with wherever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ebina, you're okay with not\Ngoing back to Akita this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gone back because\NI felt sad ringing in the new year alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But with all the fun we've been having together,\NI haven't felt lonely at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And we shall have fun indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason being... it is indeed Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylphin is pretty excited, huh?\NIt's Christmas! Christmas! Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What a child...\NIt's Christmas! Christmas! Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you celebrate Christmas at home?\NNow you, Ebina!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, correct! We do not!\N"It's Christmas"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Christmas day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm spending Christmas with Umaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,WOO-HOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you want to go see the lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,These are pretty indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing but couples here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! They're dressed like Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're selling cakes. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,they're even selling costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother sure looked pretty sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyou kara holiday! Mankitsu shichae!\NOur holiday starts today! Enjoy it to the fullest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is way more fun than I thought it would be, Alex!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Three-day weekend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't really follow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever you go, there are so many people...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone wants to do something on Christmas, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do none of you have a special someone\Nwith whom to spend this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina, do you have someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! N-no, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Kirie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,O-o-of course I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, why don't we all go back to my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have a Christmas party!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we were going to talk about relationships,\Nbut she was just inviting us over...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone spent a LOT of time decorating...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I... I think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can sit where you like, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? There's an extra cushion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Actually, one more person will be joining us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Could she mean... Alex?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've invited my good friend UMR!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:05:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,UMR?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The champion of the gaming world!\NAnd the person who gave me this badge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that badge is from a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,UMR is SO cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do? Did I promise to meet her today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's thanks to UMR that we were able\Nto get together like this today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't had many friends since coming to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after enrolling in school,\NI had little idea indeed as to how to make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, I learned the Japanese custom of\Nmaking friends by challenging others and beating them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's not right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to make friends with Umaru,\Nwhich is why I challenged her at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:07:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was UMR who taught me... you don't make friends\Nby beating them, you do it by having FUN with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And the strength of that becomes a dream\Nthat will lead to the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.42,0:07:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I ever say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was UMR's advice that let me\Nbecome friends with you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a lesson well learned:\NIf something is bothering you, just ask for advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you will regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There are indeed many, many things\Nfor UMR and I to discuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And I bet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,she decorated this room all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make sure not to wake her as we leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And YOU, Kirie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,O-oh... O-o-o-okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, till next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I had a lot of fun today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,From Sylphin...? She woke up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This was sent two hours ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! All these texts being sent\Non Christmas must be causing delays.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Umaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,UMR is SO cool! SO cool! SO COOL!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Ebina. I left something at Sylphin's house.\NAre you okay going home alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,S-sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ebina?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Taihei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you supposed to hang out with Umaru today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I was, up until a little while ago.\NBut she said she forgot something, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she just left you on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm perfectly fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we go back together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:10:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,O-okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! Look, a couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, I... I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for putting you out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to be out alone at night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If something is bothering you, just ask for advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you will regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:11:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, there's something I'd like to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well hello there, Sylphin! Merry Christmas!\NNow then, tell me what you'd like for a present. Anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho-ho-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I... I would like some Japanese friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.46,0:11:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? So, that's what you wished for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Santa seemed most disturbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The old man... I mean, even Santa\Ncouldn't make FRIENDS happen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I want some friends\NI can talk to about Japan, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ask for a computer once you're in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can talk to people from Japan\Njust by using the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my Japanese friend, Shinra Rasenken Sirius.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an impressive name indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll be able to meet him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Brother, you're going to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. I'll be going to high school there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,School... in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll be a little sad when Alex leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You two have always been close...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother's friend...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,UMH is unstoppable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That is one fearsome Japanese fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This hard-fought battle has forged mutual respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,By challenging others, one can make friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,such admirable fighting spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas, Sylphin!\NHere, it's a fighting game controller!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, made by HORU!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure has started to want some strange things...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Today was so much fun, Sylphin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I was very happy that you invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,M-m-merry Christmash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess they've all gone home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylphin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas, TSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:14:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Santa...? UMR, why are you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I saw them selling these,\Nso... d-does it look okay on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I'm late. Um, do you mind if I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a Japanese friend indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,WOO-HOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Big Brother! It's not like you\Nto hand this out first thing in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is he still half-asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Umaru. It's your New Year's allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what sorcery is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I being tested?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You don't seem happy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I got TWO of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and I sure am grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like when a vending machine messes up\Nand gives you two drinks instead of one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you, dear Consumer, pay for both?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you wouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This mistake is all on my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Take yer average ramen shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you order one bowl but you friggin' get TWO?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure feel lucky to have gotten two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, that was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But you gotta pay for that other one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, the fault now lies with YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about game arcades!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If I put in one coin but end up getting two prizes,\Nthey're both still mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just the nature of the game, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And life is like a game, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Life" is about goals and aimin' for the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is Cannalad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,More to the point, why would Big Brother\Nhave prepared TWO envelopes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he should only need one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-ha! This whole time, something has felt off.\NTwo envelopes... Big Brother spacing out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It can only mean...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Can only mean"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That he'd planned on giving two\NNew Year's allowances all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll give her two this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ebina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um, I hope I can be of help to you this year as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Um-!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um... i-is Umaru here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but... she's still asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.17,0:17:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm awake! These two are acting WEIRD!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I have a New Year's gift for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! N-no, I couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no trouble. Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:18:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's strange. I put it right here, next to Umaru's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,La-la-laaa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry it's not in an envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina said she's going to check out the New Year's sales.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,O-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Big Brother? Let's talk about vending machines...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where did Taihei go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He got called to the meeting room a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The meeting room? That's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He seemed quite happy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Your brother said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:19:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He gets all mad if I leave even a small mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,By a "small mess," does she mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Umaru, you need to put this away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It really was small.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru! I told you to clean up after yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He really is too strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,he's a good listener, and he's really kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A "listener"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! N-no, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina sure is nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All Big Brother ever does is get mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, that's not to say I'm entirely without fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It turns out Big Brother is SUPER nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me some cola and potato chips.\NOh, and more manga, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, I ate yours too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Just one more billing charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I might... actually be selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,From the outside looking in,\Nall I do is push Big Brother around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad... I have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've had a long day at work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, just have a seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaruuuuun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and welcome to the Umaru-style Space of Happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and step right in, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru, I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go on a business trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So you... you won't be coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I got chosen as a member of the project team,\Nand I'll have to go out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to come back here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You can't leave me, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You can't just leave and not come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Umaru. I'm worried about this too,\Nbut the decision has been made.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will you be gone? A month? Wait, a year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.50,0:21:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Two weeks...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If I'm gone for two weeks,\Nyou'll make a real mess around here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT'S WHAT YOU'RE WORRIED ABOUT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.00,0:21:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And, wait! What makes you think I'll make a mess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You always do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but... look, just get out and stay gone,\Nfor at least two weeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.58,0:23:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanukichi! It sure is fun to enjoy Christmas\Nwith some anime songs, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.83,0:23:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Bomba, you finally get it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I GET TO ENJOY THE SEASON EVEN THOUGH\NI DON'T HAVE A GIRLFRIEND!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,IS ANYONE OUT THERE LISTENING?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.63,0:23:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that! There are people crying\Nin front of their TVs right now!
